g.text: Consumes messages from the Position topic
Assign message to account-bin by accountID and child action-bin by event-action
(References to the messagses to be stored in bins, no duplication of messages)
Call Bin Processor with the list of account-bins
Pre fetch all transferStateChanges for all the transferIds in the account-bin
Pre fetch all position and settlement account balances for the account-bin
: Order of processing for various actions
1. Fulfil - Work in progress is first priority
2. Abort & Timeout - Freeing funds for future transfers is priority before tackling new requests
3. Prepare - Processing new requests is last priority
Input: Bin, Pre-fetched account balances and transferStateChanges
Output: Accumulated changes in position and transferStateChanges

Output: Accumulated changes in position and transferStateChanges
